{"word":"ἐπεισέρχομαι","slug":"ἐπεισέρχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπεισέρχομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> with <a href='S:aorist tense'>aor.</a> and <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>:— <i>to come in besides</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; as stepmother, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to come in after</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to come into beside</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, or <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: of things, <i>to be imported</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to come into one's head, occur to</i> one, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}